     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="3"/>
   <head>TO THE READER.</head>
   <list>
      <item>1 <hi>HE that knoweth not that he ought to knowe, is a brute beast among men.</hi>
      </item>
      <item>2 <hi>He that knoweth no more then he hath neede of, is a man among brute beastes.</hi>
      </item>
      <item>3 <hi>He that knoweth all that may be knowne, is a God among men.</hi>
      </item>
   </list>
   <list>
      <item>1 Reade willingly.</item>
      <item>2 Correct friendly.</item>
      <item>3 Iudge indifferently.</item>
   </list>
</div>
